[2] China (Guizhou)
Date: Tue 21 Feb 2017 22:55 PM CST
Source: FIC (Flu Information Centre/Flu in China) [edited]
http://www.flu.org.cn/en/news_detail?action=ql&uid=MjI0OA&pd=YXRsbXBw&newsId=19092


The medical health institution of Qiandongnan Miao and Dong autonomous prefecture [Guizhou province] found a H7N9 AIV positive sample from a unknown pneumonia case in Leishan county during the enhanced pneumonia surveillance. The test result was later confirmed by Guizhou provincial CDC.

The 51-year-old patient, lived in Leishan county of Qiandongnan Miao and Dong autonomous prefecture. The epidemiological investigation revealed that the patient had a history of contact with live poultry. The patient is now in hospital for treatment.

